This repository contains scripts and maybe other stuff for refracta linux.
http://www.ibiblio.org/refracta

A clone of the repo is included in Refracta-6.0.6 to allow you to get updated versions of some scripts or packages when they are available. It can be found at /home/github/refracta

To update the files in your local folder, open a terminal and enter the following commands:
  cd /home/github/refracta
  git pull origin master
Then, either copy the desired file into place or install any new .deb files you want.
